by **delfick755**:

<pre>Hello,

is it possible to group bound methods so we don't have to keep writing out
the name of the type we're binding to ?

For example

bind (self *T) (
    func hello() {
    }

    func there() {
    }
)

This way we have yet even less typing, and changing the name of a type will
involve less hassle.

Thankyou

Regards
Stephen</pre>
